, 2012</small>\n\n<ul>\n<li>IE8 style fix</li>\n<li>Fix for custom pages and testimonials widgets</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<small>May 2nd, 2012</small>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n]]>\n	</changelog>\n</notifier>','yes');
